    public class EasyKillBot
extends robocode.AdvancedRobot
    EasyKillBotV2 is a competitive Bot for Robocode that is in the building phase. Wins 80-100% against all included Robots, except two robots. Loses to Walls Robot 75% of the time. Ties 50% with Corners Robot.
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Justin Lee
